description: Start at the intersection near Maycheelin Asian Market and head straight down the cobblestone road. Pass The Doctors pub on the right and Greggs on the left. Continue straight; the destination, Thomas J Walls Coffee, is on the left side with a dark wooden storefront, located just before Mandi Citta.
